Directed by Surender Reddy

Written by Gopalakrishna Paruchuri. Sai Madhav Burra. Surender Reddy. Vema Reddy. Manoj Muntashir. Jitendra Pawar

Cast Chiranjeevi (Uyyalawada Narasimha Reddy). Amitabh Bachchan (Gosayi Venkanna). Sudeep (Avuku Raju). Vijay Sethupathi (Raja Pandi). Jagapathi Babu (Veera Reddy). Nayanthara (Siddhamma). Anushka Shetty (Jhansi Lakshmibai). Ravi Kishan (Basireddy). Nassar (Jayaramireddy). Lakshmi Gopalaswamy (Uyyalawada Narasimha Reddy’s mother). Mukesh Rishi (Baba Khan). Tanikella Bharani (Govindayya Sharma). Brahmaji (Obanna). Raghu Babu (Ragavachari). Rohini (Padmamma). Pavitra Lokesh (Neelamma (as Pavithra Lokesh)). Tamannaah Bhatia (Lakshmi). Santhosh Adduri (Varadareddy). Anand (Kumara Mallareddy).Saritha Anandini.Anthony. Misha Arobelidze (British Warrior).Neelya Bhavani. David Blazejko (Bounty hunter Harrison). Krishna Chaitanya (Kasim Khan). Sai Chand (Subbayya).Charandeep.Navin Etika.Gandhi.Randhir Gatla.Giri. James Graeme (Lord Macaulay). Henry (Cochrane). Indra (Jhansi Commander).Jagadish. Lasha Kankava (Russell). Raghu Kumar Karumanchi (Bullireddy). Mark Kitto (Inglis). Niharika Konidela (Bhagyam). Meka Rama Krishna (Jangam Mallayya).Kandala Sravan Kumar.Meghna. Henry Maynard (Cochrane (uncredited)) . Praveen Dacharam (Boya). Jambul Gogia (British soldier). Jambul Gogia (British soldier). Waqar Khan (British Officer).Rose Laskar.Duvvasi Mohan. Raghav Rudra Mulpuru (Aswathama (priest)). Jabardasth Naveen (Sheshu drinker). Prudhviraj (Madhavayyar). Mirko Quaini (British officer).Ramaraju. Ranadheer (Narsireddy). Mark Rathbone (British Official). Ajay Ratnam (Mallareddy).Ramana Reddy.Sana. Kumanan Sethuraman ((as Kumunan Sethuraman)).Shivam.Nadella Siddhartha. Oscar Skagerberg(Jackson). Krish Soni (Child Unr). Rudra Soni (Child Unr).Pavan Suresh.Krishna Teja. Vaja Tsiklauri (Soldier). Jenny Umbhau (Warrior Woman).Paata Uttej.Vijay. Prem Vinny (Basavayya).Veera Ravi Kumar Yalla. Daniel O’Kane (Actor (uncredited)). Alexx O’Nell (Watson (uncredited)). Terence J. Rotolo (Actor (uncredited)). Matthew Stirling(Daniel (uncredited))

Languages Telugu

Producers Farhan Akhtar. Sunny Bhatti. Narravula Gopi Krishna. George Melikishvili. V.Y. Praveenkumar. Vakada Appa Rao. Amrit Sawhney. Ritesh Sidhwani. Ram Charan Teja. Koppineedi Vidya

Production Konidela Production Company
